Maintainer: Emily A. Robinson <erobin17@calpoly.edu>
Description: 'You Draw It' is a feature that allows users to interact with a chart
  directly by drawing a line on their computer screen with a mouse. Originally introduced
  by the New York Times in 2015 for the purpose of interactive reading, this package adapts
  the use of the 'You Draw It' method as a tool for interactive testing of graphics.
